  <li><strong>Phishing &amp; Email Security</strong> - Learn how scammers use fake emails and how to identify and stop them.</li>
  <li><strong>Ransomware &amp; Backup</strong> - Understand how ransomware works and how strong backups can be your lifesaver.</li>
  <li><strong>Passwords, MFA &amp; Account Security</strong> - Develop better password practices and use multi-factor authentication effectively.</li>
