  <li><strong>Social Engineering &amp; AI Threats</strong> - Learn how to recognize deepfakes, voice cloning, and modern manipulation tactics.</li>
  <li><strong>Staff Awareness &amp; Training</strong> - Build a cybersecurity-aware culture without overwhelming your team.</li>
</ul>

<p>Final Thoughts</p>

<p>Cybersecurity is not just an IT responsibility, it’s a business-wide commitment. Small practices that prioritize digital security not only avoid regulatory penalties but also gain a competitive advantage by building trust with their clients.</p>

